    Another way to convert

    library(readxl)

widdee_data <- read_xlsx("data/Lab1_data.xlsx")
#> New names:
#> * `` -> ...1
#> * `` -> ...3
#> * `` -> ...4
#> * `` -> ...5
#> * `` -> ...6
#> * ...

widdee_data <- widdee_data %>% pivot_longer(
  cols = 2:13,
  names_to = c("Loudness", "Time", "Letter"),
  names_pattern = "(.*)_(.*)_(.*)",
  values_to = "DV"
  
)
#> Error in widdee_data %>% pivot_longer(cols = 2:13, names_to = c("Loudness", : could not find function "%>%"
